title: Delivery Man From Murim
description: Delivery Man From Murim Manhwa The martial god of the Murim becomes a super-fast delivery man! Before even reaching the age of forty, the martial god “Kang So” had conquered the world. While he was in the midst of consolidating his energy after reaching enlightenment, he suddenly descended into a newly formed rift… He arrives in 21st century South Korea, a land desolated by gates and demonic beasts. Here, the martial god from the martial world, now a delivery man, shall bring peace! The Delivery Man From Moorim The Delivery Man From Murim 무림에서 온 배달부
